text: The coffee, especially hot latte wasn't impressive and could have been better. However, the ramen corndog was amazing! Totally packs a punch when eaten with hot sauce. The staff members were friendly, and they allowed pets inside. Since we arrived early, it wasn't hot, so we decided to sit outside. The best is, they open as early as 8am, which is rare around Iskandar!
Instead of the usual chinese breakfast, we went over to SongJeong Corndog to try out the food. No regrets, the corndogs are awesome, and the ice tea with coffee bear is so cute.

Went there with my husband on the 16th April, Food and Drinks were amazing!! Service from the staffs were friendly and welcoming. Great Smile from them too!! Handling of food very hygiene and store is clean!! Keep it upüòÑüëç
